trans-unit.source: Creates and deletes Internet Information Services (IIS) 6.0 virtual roots.
trans-unit.target: Crea y elimina raíces virtuales de Internet Information Services (IIS) 6.0.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapIISVRoot> interface defines methods for creating and deleting virtual roots in IIS 6.0.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapIISVRoot> interfaz define métodos para crear y eliminar las raíces virtuales en IIS 6.0.

trans-unit.source: This interface is implemented only by the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot> class and is used only within the .NET Framework infrastructure while creating a SOAP-enabled COM+ application virtual root.
trans-unit.target: Esta interfaz se implementa solo el <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot> clase y se utiliza solo dentro de la infraestructura de .NET Framework durante la creación de una raíz virtual de aplicación COM + con SOAP habilitado.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapIISVRoot> does not need to be implemented directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapIISVRoot> no es necesario para que se implementen directamente en el código.

trans-unit.source: Instead, use the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> class, which implements the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher> interface that contains the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.CreateVirtualRoot%2A> and <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.DeleteVirtualRoot%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: En su lugar, use la <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish> de la clase, que implementa el <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher> interfaz que contiene el <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.CreateVirtualRoot%2A> y <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.DeleteVirtualRoot%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.source: However, <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.DeleteVirtualRoot%2A> is not fully implemented by <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>.
trans-unit.target: Sin embargo, <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.DeleteVirtualRoot%2A> no está totalmente implementado por <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish>.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot> is used internally by the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot> se utiliza internamente por .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: You do not need to use it directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: No es necesario utilizar directamente en el código.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot" />.

trans-unit.source: A string with the value <c>"IIS://localhost/W3SVC/1/ROOT"</c> representing the root Web server.
trans-unit.target: Cadena con el valor <c>"IIS://localhost/W3SVC/1/ROOT"</c> que representa el servidor web raíz.

trans-unit.source: The physical path of the virtual root, which corresponds to <c>PhysicalPath</c> from the <see cref="M:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.CreateVirtualRoot(System.String,System.String,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Ruta de acceso física de la raíz virtual, que corresponde a <c>PhysicalPath</c> del método <see cref="M:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.CreateVirtualRoot(System.String,System.String,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@)" />.

trans-unit.source: The name of the virtual root, which corresponds to <c>VirtualRoot</c> from <see cref="M:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.CreateVirtualRoot(System.String,System.String,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@)" />.
trans-unit.target: Nombre de la raíz virtual, que corresponde a <c>VirtualRoot</c> de <see cref="M:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.CreateVirtualRoot(System.String,System.String,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@,System.String@)" />.

trans-unit.source: A string to which an error message can be written.
trans-unit.target: Cadena en la que puede escribirse un mensaje de error.

trans-unit.source: Creates an Internet Information Services (IIS) virtual root.
trans-unit.target: Crea una raíz virtual de Internet Information Services (IIS).

trans-unit.source: You do not need to call the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot.Create%2A> method from your code.
trans-unit.target: No es necesario llamar a la <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot.Create%2A> método desde el código.

trans-unit.source: Instead, use the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.CreateVirtualRoot%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: En su lugar, use la <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.CreateVirtualRoot%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: The root Web server, as specified by <c>RootWebServer</c> from the <see cref="M:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.DeleteVirtualRoot(System.String,System.String,System.String@)" /> method.
trans-unit.target: Servidor web raíz, especificado por <c>RootWebServer</c> del método <see cref="M:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IComSoapPublisher.DeleteVirtualRoot(System.String,System.String,System.String@)" />.

trans-unit.source: The physical path of the virtual root.
trans-unit.target: Ruta de acceso física de la raíz virtual.

trans-unit.source: The name of the virtual root.
trans-unit.target: Nombre de la raíz virtual.

trans-unit.source: A string to which an error message can be written.
trans-unit.target: Cadena en la que puede escribirse un mensaje de error.

trans-unit.source: Deletes an Internet Information Services (IIS) virtual root.
trans-unit.target: Elimina una raíz virtual de Internet Information Services (IIS).

trans-unit.source: Even though it is public, the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot.Delete%2A> method is not intended to be called directly.
trans-unit.target: Aunque es pública, la <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.IISVirtualRoot.Delete%2A> método no está pensado para ser llamado directamente.

trans-unit.source: Alternatively, there is the <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.DeleteVirtualRoot%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Como alternativa, hay el <xref:System.EnterpriseServices.Internal.Publish.DeleteVirtualRoot%2A> método.

trans-unit.source: However, this method is not fully implemented.
trans-unit.target: Sin embargo, este método no está totalmente implementado.
